She didn't even hear the door being knocked on.  she was muttering 
about losing her mind and might having to be reprogrammed.  She paced 
the floor in her room. She couldn't get over how she heard Phobia 
when Phobia wasn't even around.  It just blasted her mind on how that 
was possable.
